# n8n Workflow Naming Convention

## Terminology

| Term | Where it shows | Format |
|------|----------------|--------|
| **Filename** | File explorer / disk | `{company}-{short-description}.json` |
| **Workflow name** | Inside JSON `"name"` field / n8n UI | `{COMPANY} \| {Category} \| {short-description}` |

## Filename Format

All workflow JSON files should be named using this pattern:

```
{company}-{short-description}.json
```

Example: `tner-auto-fix-reconciliation.json`

## Workflow Name Format

The **workflow name** (inside the JSON `"name"` field) should follow:

```
{COMPANY} | {Category} | {short-description}
```

Example: `TNER | Admin | auto-fix-reconciliation`

## Companies

