| Code |
|------|
| `HOZ` |
| `TNER` |
| `WRAP` |

## Components

| Component | Description | Example |
|-----------|-------------|---------|
| **COMPANY** | Uppercase company code (HOZ, TNER, WRAP) | `HOZ`, `TNER`, `WRAP` |
| **Category** | The folder/workflow category | `Vendor-operation`, `Admin`, `Sales` |
| **Short Description** | Brief purpose | `gate-supplier`, `admin-dashboard` |

