## Folder Structure

```
workflows/
├── admin/             # Administrative work: emails, data sorting, personal scheduling
├── customer-service/  # After-sales support, customer issues, support tickets
├── finance/           # Xero, invoicing, accounting
├── human-resources/   # HR workflows, employee management
├── legal/             # Legal documents, contracts, compliance
├── marketing/         # Campaigns, promotions, social media, product scrapers
├── operations/        # Job scheduling, ServiceM8
├── sales/             # Sales consultation, prospecting, lead management
├── shopify/           # E-commerce integrations
├── technology/        # Internal workflows to improve efficiency
├── utils/             # Generic utility workflows
└── vendor-operation/  # Supplier/vendor workflows
```
